OL,3,CResidents return after being evacuated
OL,4,Cfrom homes due to smell of gas
OL,6,FResidents have returned to a block of
OL,7,Fflats in Jersey after some reported
OL,8,Fsmelling gas.
OL,10,FEmergency services and the gas company
OL,11,FIsland Energy were called to Cherry
OL,12,FOrchard Court on Valley Road in St
OL,13,FHelier on Wednesday morning (1 July),
OL,14,Fwith homes evacuated as they assessed
OL,15,Fa suspected gas leak.
OL,17,FA police cordon was put in place with
OL,18,Fpeople asked to avoid the area while
OL,19,Finvestigations were carried out -
OL,20,Fdisplaced residents were evacuated to
OL,21,FSt Saviour's Parish Hall.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
