OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1783698492
OL,3,CResidents return after being evacuated
OL,4,Cfrom homes due to smell of gas
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News, one explained:
OL,7,F"I got up to let the dog out and a
OL,8,Ffirefighter popped his head over the
OL,9,Ffence and said to evacuate. Our pets
OL,10,Fhad to stay behind.
OL,12,F"When I opened my front door, the
OL,13,Fsmell of gas was very intense."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
