OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1783698492
OL,3,CResidents return after being evacuated
OL,4,Cfrom homes due to smell of gas
OL,6,FIn a statement, the Government of
OL,7,FJersey's Justice and Home Affairs
OL,8,Fdepartment says: "The States of Jersey
OL,9,FFire and Rescue Service were called to
OL,10,Fsupport Island Energy this morning at
OL,11,FCherry Orchard Court, Valley Road,
OL,12,Ffollowing two separate reports of a
OL,13,Fsmell of gas in the area, just after
OL,14,F8:30am.
OL,16,F"A number of residents were evacuated
OL,17,Fas a precaution."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
