CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1783698492
OL,3,CResidents return after being evacuated
OL,4,Cfrom homes due to smell of gas
OL,6,FIn a statement released at just after
OL,7,F4:30pm on Wednesday, Island Energy
OL,8,Fexplains: "No readings were found that
OL,9,Fwould have required an evacuation of
OL,10,Fthe building.
OL,12,F"The team carried out an extended
OL,13,Fsearch beyond the perimeter and found
OL,14,Fa minor gas escape that posed no
OL,15,Fsafety risk which the team are dealing
OL,16,Fwith.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
