OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1783698492
OL,3,CResidents return after being evacuated
OL,4,Cfrom homes due to smell of gas
OL,6,F"We would like to take this
OL,7,Fopportunity to remind islanders that
OL,8,Fif they smell gas or suspect a gas
OL,9,Fescape to call our 24-hour emergency
OL,10,Fline on 01534 755555."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/5
